original_title: ETs Among Us 6: My Cosmic Journey - Revelations of a Psychic CEO
overview: Unusually gifted, successful CEO/entrepreneur Sebastien Martin has experienced accurate prophetic visions for years. While ignoring his psychic abilities to build a normal life, Sebastien's shocking memories of his alien past intensified after a strange encounter with an Annunaki ET claiming to be his soul brother - leading to a profound journey of self-discovery and an urgent message to humanity.
title: ETs Among Us 6: My Cosmic Journey - Revelations of a Psychic CEO
